<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Security Alert: Password Changed</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f7f6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
        .header { background: #1e293b; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; color: #fff; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; }
        .content { padding: 40px; }
        .alert-icon { font-size: 48px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #f59e0b; }
        .info-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fef3c7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; color: #92400e; }
        .footer { padding: 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6; }
        .highlight { font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Security Notification</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="alert-icon">🔒</div>
            <p>This is a notification that the password for your company account <span class="highlight">{{companyName}}</span> was recently changed. Your updated login credentials are below:</p>
            
            <div class="credentials-box" style="background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #1e293b;">
                <p style="margin: 8px 0;"><span style="font-weight: 600; color: #475569;">Company Code:</span> <span style="font-family: monospace; background: #f1f5f9; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 4px;">{{companyCode}}</span></p>
                <p style="margin: 8px 0;"><span style="font-weight: 600; color: #475569;">New Password:</span> <span style="font-family: monospace; background: #f1f5f9; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 4px; color: #1e293b; font-weight: bold;">{{password}}</span></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>If you performed this action:</strong> You can safely ignore this email.</p>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #ef4444; font-weight: 600;">If you did not change your password:</p>
            <p>Please contact our support team immediately to secure your account. Your security is our top priority.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Raftaar HRMS. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated security notification.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
